if [ -n "$GITHUB_PAT" ]; then export GH_TOKEN="$GITHUB_PAT"; fi && gh pr create --title "feat: #1 - Account Management - Open Trades & Order History" --body "$(cat <<'EOF'
## Summary

Implements a comprehensive Account page displaying open trades and complete transaction trade history, addressing issue #1.

## Implementation Plan

See [implementation plan](specs/issue-1-adw-bfd1a7d1-sdlc_planner-account-open-trades-order-history.md) for detailed specifications.

## Changes Made

### Backend
- **API Endpoints**: Created `/api/account/open-trades` and `/api/account/order-history` endpoints
- **Data Models**: Enhanced OpenTrade model with comprehensive trade information
- **OpenFX Integration**: Integrated with OpenFX API for fetching open trades and order history
- **Error Handling**: Implemented robust error handling and logging

### Frontend
- **Account Page**: Created dedicated Account page component with tabbed interface
- **Open Trades View**: Real-time display of active positions with P&L tracking
- **Order History**: Complete transaction history with filtering and sorting
- **Consistent Styling**: Applied style guide for consistent UI/UX across components

### Testing & Documentation
- **API Tests**: Added comprehensive tests for account endpoints
- **Integration Tests**: Validated OpenFX API integration
- **E2E Tests**: Created end-to-end tests for Account page functionality

## ADW Tracking
ID: bfd1a7d1

Closes #1
EOF
)" --base main
